5.1 CSS Animation
  - <transition></transition>
  - v-enter
    - opacity 3s
  - v-enter-active
    - transition: opacity 3s
  - v-enter-to
  - v-leave
  - v-leave-active
  - v-leave-to

5.2 animate.css
  -https://animate.style/
  
5.3 multi style + animate
  - animate css -> @keyframes
  - transition
  - type/duration

5.4 JS animate/Velocity.js
  - js Animation hook
    - @before-enter
    - <transition @before-enter="functions"></transition>
    - var -> element(el)
      -> el.style.color='red';
    - @enter 
    - var -> el,done
      -> done() event. control when is done
      -> fire after enter
    - @after-enter
    - @before-leave,@leave,@after-leave
  - Velocity.js
    -http://www.velocityjs.org/

5.5 multi components Animation
  - v-if/v-else
  - <transition mode="in-out"></transition>
  - pick a mode
